thread.title: barbara crane

author: barbara crane
title: barbara crane
text: Always cheaper than the beauticians and the BIG department stores even Duty Free --- free shipping is a bonus and I usually can buy all the products I use without having to wait for a back order. I have been with Strawberry Net for over ten years and found the delivery quick easy and packaging is usually tight especially around the liquid products. Although last time I ordered the deodorant Payot product all leaked - I didn't complain because it really is a small thing to complain about and there is far too much of this in our world. Be happy we can obtain good quality products at a very good price for free delivery.
